suncertify.db
Class DBDataModel

java.lang.Object
  suncertify.db.DBDataModel
Direct Known Subclasses:
DatabaseManager
public class DBDataModel
extends java.lang.Object

This Object is the model for the database file record, it interacts with the Database file directly. It manages the reading(initialisation) of records in the database file and the writing back of the record to the designated file in the proper required format

Author:
Segun

public void writeToDatabaseFile(java.util.List<java.lang.String[]> m)
                         throws URLyBirdException

m - - List that contains an array of String, which each array of string represents a row of data in the record is not allowed to write into the file

URLyBirdException - If any exception occurs when trying to write the List of records back to the database file
